Below are both the Python code and insights from a basic exploratory analysis of "hour" data. 
This dataset was provided by bradfordtuckfield.com, and represents real data from a bike rental service in Washington D.C.
I am performing an exploratory analysis to understand the data and gain high-level insights. 


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

