# Right from the jump, average ridership increased substantially from 2011 (yr 0) - 2012 (yr 1)
# Average ridership on specific changed from year-to-year as well. In 2011, The highest average ridership day was Wednesday. In 2012, it was Friday. 
# Promotions & Scheduling maintenance can be determined with this information.

